          result: "     1→# AI Partner Business Context\n     2→\n     3→Quick onboarding document for AI. Baseline date：2026-03-31。\n     4→\n     5→## Scope\n     6→\n     7→AI Partner is an AI partner product that interacts with bosses through IM (Tencent IM Work groups). Frontend and backend in the same repo, three-layer test coverage。\n     8→\n     9→| Layer | Module | Description |\n    10→|----|------|------|\n    11→| Frontend | `packages-pc/hddr` | Vue 3 + Vite，Boss and Claw two routing domains |\n    12→| HTTP API | `aicenterapi` | Gateway, frontend-facing |\n    13→| WebSocket | `meetingwsapi` | Real-time meeting audio and transcription |\n    14→| RPC Core | `hd_ai_search` | DB / IM / LLM all here |\n    15→| E2E server | `test/e2e/server` | Standalone test backend, reuses production handlers |\n    16→\n    17→Three main business lines：**Meeting Analysis**、**Report Analysis**、**Article Analysis**。All interact with bosses through IM group messages。\n    18→\n    19→---\n    20→\n    21→## Architecture Overview\n    22→\n    23→```\n    24→Frontend (Browser)\n    25→├── /boss/*          Boss entry pages (meetings/reports/articles)\n    26→├── /claw/*          Claw IM main UI (message list/sub-sessions/memory management)\n    27→├── Create meeting → POST /api/meetings\n    28→├── Real-time recording → WS /ws/meet/:meeting_id\n    29→├── Send report → POST /chat/im/report\n    30→├── Send article → POST /chat/im/article\n    31→└── IM Group interaction → Tencent IM SDK\n    32→         │\n    33→    ┌────┴────┐          ┌──────────────┐\n    34→    │aicenterapi│          │ meetingwsapi │\n    35→    │ (HTTP)    │          │ (WebSocket)  │\n    36→    └────┬────┘          └──────┬───────┘\n    37→         │    RPC calls          │\n    38→         └────────┬─────────────┘\n    39→                  ▼\n    40→         ┌────────────────┐\n    41→         │  hd_ai_search  │\n    42→         │    (RPC)       │\n    43→         │ ├─ imchat      │ ← IM callback dispatch + streaming reply\n    44→         │ ├─ meeting     │ ← meeting analysis pipeline\n    45→         │ ├─ report      │ ← report analysis pipeline\n    46→         │ ├─ article     │ ← article analysis pipeline\n    47→         │ ├─ thread_memory│ ← person memory\n    48→         │ ├─ boss_profile_memory│ ← boss profile storage & sync\n    49→         │ ├─ ai_coach    │ ← AI Coach\n    50→         │ ├─ agent       │ ← Agent orchestration\n    51→         │ └─ memory      │ ← general memory\n    52→         └────────┬───────┘\n    53→              ┌───┼───┐\n    54→              ▼   ▼   ▼\n    55→           MySQL Redis Tencent IM  LLM(Volcano/Azure)\n    56→\n    57→common/shared/                ← shared data source for frontend and backend\n    58→├── reaction_emoji.json       ← Emoji mapping (Go embed + frontend import)\n    59→└── user_relation.json        ← user relationship options\n    60→\n    61→Test Layers\n    62→├── Layer 1: go test -tags integration  ← Sandbox MySQL + miniredis + Mock IM/LLM\n    63→├── Layer 2: vitest / Cypress component ← Real Vue components，Mock HTTP/TIM\n    64→└── Layer 3: Cypress E2E + E2E server   ← Real routes + real IM callback\n    65→```\n    66→\n    67→---\n    68→\n    69→## Frontend Architecture\n    70→\n    71→### Tech Stack\n    72→\n    73→| Layer | Technology |\n    74→|----|------|\n    75→| Framework | Vue 3.5 + TypeScript |\n    76→| Build | Vite 7 |\n    77→| State Management | Pinia 2（SessionStorage persistence） |\n    78→| UI Component Library | Naive UI 2 |\n    79→| CSS | UnoCSS + Tailwind |\n    80→| HTTP Client | Alova 2（`aiAlova` instance） |\n    81→| IM SDK | @tencentcloud/lite-chat 4.2 |\n    82→| WebSocket | @vueuse/core `useWebSocket` |\n    83→| Audio Capture | Web Audio API（ScriptProcessorNode + PCM encoding） |\n    84→\n    85→### Code Locations\n    86→\n    87→```\n    88→packages-pc/hddr/src/\n    89→├── boss/                  ← Boss business pages & components\n    90→│   ├── api.ts             ← HTTP API calls\n    91→│   ├── store.ts           ← Pinia store（useBossStore）\n    92→│   ├── types.ts           ← Type definitions\n    93→│   ├── record.ts          ← Audio recording hook（useAudioRecorder，module-level singleton）\n    94→│   ├── index.vue          ← Homepage (three cards: meetings/reports/articles)\n    95→│   ├── chat.vue           ← Chat interface\n    96→│   ├── history.vue        ← Session history list\n    97→│   ├── relationship.vue   ← Contact management\n    98→│   ├── preview.vue        ← Preview page\n    99→│   ├── __tests__/         ← vitest Unit tests\n   100→│   └── components/        ← Sub-components\n   101→│\n   102→├── claw/                  ← Claw IM Integration layer\n   103→│   ├── api.ts             ← IM API（user_sig / report / article / onboarding）\n   104→│   ├── store.ts           ← Pinia store（useClawStore，Composition API）\n   105→│   ├── store-modules/     ← store Sub-modules\n   106→│   │   ├── sessions.ts    ← Session list & message management\n   107→│   │   ├── meeting.ts     ← Meeting state\n   108→│   │   ├── partner.ts     ← AI AI partner persona\n   109→│   │   ├── article-resources.ts ← Article resources\n   110→│   │   ├── memory-assumptions.ts ← Assumption memory management\n   111→│   │   ├── user-relations.ts   ← User relations\n   112→│   │   ├── ui.ts          ← UI Layout state\n   113→│   │   └── shared.ts      ← Shared state\n   114→│   ├── types.ts           ← IM Message type definitions（emoji/relationship options from common/shared/*.json import）\n   115→│   ├── sub-session-card-actions.ts ← Card button operations（disableCardAction / keepOnlySelectedCardAction）\n   116→│   ├── im/\n   117→│   │   ├── tim.ts         ← TIM SDK singleton (create/login/event dispatch)\n   118→│   │   ├── group.ts       ← Group operations (history/send/format/reactions)\n   119→│   │   └── config.ts      ← group ID ↔ sessionId encoding/decoding\n   120→│   ├── index.vue          ← Main page"
