submitreport（content + files） |\n   165→| `/chat/im/article` | POST | submitarticle（URL / content / hotarticle ID） |\n   166→| `/chat/im/hot_article/list` | GET | hotarticlecolumntable |\n   167→| `/chat/boss/onboarding/submit` | POST | partner onboarding submission |\n   168→| `/chat/boss/partner_profile/upsert` | POST | morenewpartner profile |\n   169→| `/chat/bind_speaker_person` | POST | speaker bindingperson memory |\n   170→\n   171→### State Management\n   172→\n   173→**useBossStore**（`boss/store.ts`）：\n   174→\n   175→```typescript\n   176→state: {\n   177→  currentMeetingInfo: MeetingDetailInfo | null\n   178→  isRelationshipInitialized: boolean\n   179→  hotArticles: { id, title, image }[]\n   180→}\n   181→getters: {\n   182→  currentMeetingId, currentMeetingSessionId, onRecording\n   183→}\n   184→actions: {\n   185→  startMeeting(), getHotArticles()\n   186→}\n   187→// persistenceto SessionStorage\n   188→```\n   189→\n   190→**useClawStore**（`claw/store.ts`）：Composition API store，aggregatecombineSub-modules：\n   191→\n   192→- `sessions` — willtalkcolumntable、message、sub-sessionmanagement\n   193→- `meeting` — Meeting state\n   194→- `partner` — AI AI partner personaconfiguration\n   195→- `article-resources` — Article resources\n   196→- `user-relations` — User relations\n   197→- `ui` — UI Layout state\n   198→- `shared` — Shared state\n   199→\n   200→### Tencent IM SDK integration\n   201→\n   202→**SDK initialize**（`claw/im/tim.ts`）：\n   203→\n   204→```\n   205→getChatSDK()          ← lazycreate TencentCloudChat singleton\n   206→ensureTimReady(userId) ← login + etcwait SDK_READY\n   207→  → getImUserSig(userId) → { user_sig, user_id, main_session_id }\n   208→  → sdk.login({ userID, userSig })\n   209→  → return { sdk, mainSessionId, onboarded, partnerName, partnerAvatar }\n   210→```\n   211→\n   212→**eventseparatesend**：SDK listen `MESSAGE_RECEIVED` / `MESSAGE_MODIFIED`，unifiedthrough `dispatchIncoming` separatesend：\n   213→\n   214→1. parse `payload.data` JSON\n   215→2. `typing_state` → `typingHandlers`（notentermessagestream）\n   216→3. `reaction_action` → `reactionHandlers`\n   217→4. generalthroughgroupmessage → `convertTimMessage` → `incomingHandlers`\n   218→\n   219→alsolisten `GROUP_LIST_UPDATED` / `TOPIC_CREATED` / `TOPIC_DELETED` → `groupLifecycleHandlers`。\n   220→\n   221→**group ID ↔ sessionId encoding/decoding**（`claw/im/config.ts`）：\n   222→\n   223→- main session groupId directlythroughpass（`_mainGroupId`）\n   224→- sub-session：`groupIdToSessionId(groupId)` = base64url(groupId)\n   225→- reversetoward：`sessionIdToGroupId(sessionId)` = base64url_decode + round-trip validation\n   226→\n   227→**groupoperation**（`claw/im/group.ts`）：\n   228→\n   229→| function | Description |\n   230→|------|------|\n   231→| `getGroupList()` | obtaingetalreadyjoingroupcolumntable（filter `hddi_` beforesuffix） |\n   232→| `getGroupHistory(groupId, cursor?)` | pullgethistorymessage（50 entry/page） |\n   233→| `sendGroupText(groupId, text)` | sendgrouptextthismessage |\n   234→| `sendGroupOnlineCustomMessage(groupId, data)` | send online-only visible custom messages |\n   235→| `updateGroupProfile({ groupID, name })` | morenewgroupmaterials |\n   236→| `quitGroup(groupID)` / `dismissGroup(groupID)` | withdrawgroup / dissolvegroup |\n   237→| `fetchMessageReactions(rawMessageList)` | batch pull emoji reactions |\n   238→| `addTimMessageReaction` / `removeTimMessageReaction` | add/delete emoji reaction |\n   239→"
