leton `MeetingWebSocketManager`，management `WS /ws/meet/{meeting_id}` connection。\n   268→\n   269→**messagetype**（`MeetingMessageTypeEnum`）：\n   270→\n   271→| methodtoward | type | Description |\n   272→|------|------|------|\n   273→| → serviceend | `Ping` | heartbeat |\n   274→| → serviceend | `Welcome` | welcome/handshakemessage |\n   275→| → serviceend | `EditSpeaker` | morenewspeaker info |\n   276→| → serviceend | `EditSummary` | morenewwillmeetingsummary |\n   277→| → serviceend | `Mark` | mark transcription highlights |\n   278→| → serviceend | `RecordStatus` | recording state control |\n   279→| → serviceend | `AIInquire` | AI follow-up |\n   280→| → serviceend | `UserQuestion` | useuser to AI ask |\n   281→| ← Frontend | `Pong` | heartbeatresponse |\n   282→| ← Frontend | `Transcript` | ASR transcriptionresult |\n   283→| ← Frontend | `AI` / `AIStream` | AI analysisresult / streamstyletransportexit |\n   284→| ← Frontend | `QuestionAnswered` | AI Q&A complete |\n   285→| ← Frontend | `MeetingUpdate` | Meeting statemorenew |\n   286→| ← Frontend | `MeetingEnded` | willmeetingend |\n   287→| ← Frontend | `RecordStatusChanged` | recordingstatuschanges |\n   288→| ← Frontend | `SpeakerUpdated` | speaker updatednew |\n   289→| ← Frontend | `Marked` | transcription highlights marked |\n   290→| ← Frontend | `SummaryUpdated` | summaryalreadymorenew |\n   291→| ← Frontend | `ScoreNotEnough` | accumulateseparatenotsufficient |\n   292→| ← Frontend | `ScoreModified` | accumulateseparatechange |\n   293→| ← Frontend | `Error` | errormessage |\n   294→\n   295→**request-responsepattern**（`useWsRequest`）：through `trace_id` associaterequestandresponse，supportstimeout（default 10s）。\n   296→\n   297→### audio recording（useAudioRecorder）\n   298→\n   299→module-level singleton，bitat `boss/record.ts`。\n   300→\n   301→- sample rate 16kHz（Tongyi Tingwu ASR shouldrequest），16-bit PCM，mono\n   302→- Firefox compatible：auto-detect actual sample rate and linearly interpolate to resample\n   303→- statusmachine：`Waiting → Running ⇄ Paused → Stopped`，silence detection（default 30s）\n   304→\n   305→### environmentvariable\n   306→\n   307→| variable | usepath |\n   308→|------|------|\n   309→| `VITE_HDDI_WS` | WebSocket endpoint（willmeeting real-time connection） |\n   310→| `VITE_TC_WEBIM_APPID` | Tencent IM SDK AppID |\n   311→\n   312→---\n   313→\n   314→## willconversation model\n   315→\n   316→all interactions happen on Tencent IM **Work group（Private）** in。group ID = `chat_session.session_id`。\n   317→\n   318→### session_type\n   319→\n   320→| value | type | Description |\n   321→|----|------|------|\n   322→| 0 | regular chat | nosub-session |\n   323→| 2 | Meeting Analysis | sub-session，hanginmain sessionbelow |\n   324→| 3 | Report Analysis | sub-session |\n   325→| 4 | Article Analysis | sub-session |\n   326→| 5 | IM main session | boss's main chat window |\n   327→\n   328→### group ID format\n   329→\n   330→- main session：`hddi_<env>_main_<md5>`\n   331→- sub-session：`hddi_<env>_session_<md5>`\n   332→- `env`：`p`（production）/ `t`（test）/ `e2e`（E2E test）\n   333→\n   334→### main session vs sub-session\n   335→\n   336→the main session is the boss's primary chat window。sub-session is each analysis task（willmeeting/report/article）createstandalone IM group。\n   337→\n   338→display sub-session status notifications in main session（`session_system`）andentrycard（`session_card`）。sub-sessionindisplay AI analysisresultcard。\n   339→\n   340→---\n   341→\n   342→## business line one：Boss Meeting Analysis\n   343→\n   344→### complete lifecycle\n   345→\n   346→```\n   347→Create meeting → Real-time recording → [addquantityanalysis ×N] → endwillmeeting → mostendanalysis → IM card\n   348→```\n   349→\n   350→### Phase 1：Create meeting\n   351→\n   352→**entry**：`POST /api/meetings`（aicenterapi）\n   353→\n   354→```\n   355→aicenterapi.CreateMeetingLogic\n   356→  → hd_ai_search.CreateMeeting RPC\n   357→    → create meeting row + asr_t