          result: "   360→```\n   361→\n   362→willmeetingtype：`meeting_type=1`（BOSS）。onlyhas BOSS typego IM analysisflow。\n   363→\n   364→### Phase 2：Real-time recording（WebSocket）\n   365→\n   366→**entry**：`GET /ws/meet/:meeting_id`（meetingwsapi）\n   367→\n   368→```\n   369→WebSocket connectionbuildestablish\n   370→  → autowill BOSS Meeting statefrom NOT_STARTED → IN_PROGRESS\n   371→  → startup TranscriptManager（ASR real-time transcription）\n   372→  → receive audio frame → send ASR → storetranscriptionto DB\n   373→  → real-time push transcription results toFrontend\n   374→```\n   375→\n   376→**addquantityanalysis**：willmeeting progressrowin，`meetingwsapi` each 10 minute scheduled trigger：\n   377→\n   378→```\n   379→meetingwsapi.bossMeetingProxyTimer\n   380→  → hd_ai_search.ImChat RPC (meeting_id, since_transcript_id=N, is_final=false)\n   381→    → aipartnerMeetingAnalysisIncremental()\n   382→      → runC02AMerge()（sectionaccumulated landingadd，notexitcard）\n   383→      → persistence rolling state to agent_task_step\n   384→```\n   385→\n   386→### Phase 3：endwillmeeting & mostendanalysis\n   387→\n   388→**entry**：`POST /api/meetings/:meeting_id/end`（aicenterapi）\n   389→\n   390→```\n   391→aicenterapi.EndMeetingLogic\n   392→  → hd_ai_search.UpdateMeetingStatus(COMPLETED)\n   393→  → return（aftercontinueasync）\n   394→\n   395→meetingwsapi receivetoendevent\n   396→  → NotifyMeetingSessionRunning RPC（ifalsonotcreate IM willtalk）\n   397→  → stopBossMeetingProxyTimer()\n   398→  → hd_ai_search.ImChat RPC (meeting_id, is_final=true)\n   399→    → aipartnerMeetingAnalysisFinal()\n   400→```\n   401→\n   402→### AI analysis Pipeline（C02A → C06）\n   403→\n   404→```\n   405→C02A Merge（plain text LLM）→ C02A Final（plain text LLM）\n   406→  → C03（JSON: findings / blind spots）‖ C04（JSON: person cards）\n   407→  → C06（JSON: title + push message）\n   408→  → [optional] C07（deep talk per speaker）/ C08（signal deep talk）\n   409→```\n   410→\n   411→eachstepthrough `meetingTaskRunner` management（create `agent_task` + `agent_task_step` row）。\n   412→\n   413→### fourkindanalysischildflow\n   414→\n   415→| entryitem | childflow | IM notification |\n   416→|------|--------|---------|\n   417→| `since=0, final=true` | oneshot | send RUNNING → analysis → sendcard → DONE |\n   418→| `since=0, final=false` | first | notsend（onlycreate rolling state） |\n   419→| `since>0, final=false` | incremental | notsend（onlymorenew rolling state） |\n   420→| `since>0, final=true` | final | send RUNNING → analysis → sendcard → DONE |\n   421→\n   422→### Finalize messageorder\n   423→\n   424→1. `sendMeetingSessionInputToSubSession`（first message of sub-session）\n   425→2. `sendMeetingThreadBundle`（AI analysiscard）\n   426→3. `updateSubSessionGroupProfile`（morenewgroupnamecalledandintro）\n   427→4. `modifyMainSessionSystemStatus(DONE)`\n   428→5. `SendGroupCustomMessageWithResult`（main session session_card）\n   429→6. `UpdateMainSessionCardMsgSeq`（persistencecard MsgSeq）\n   430→\n   431→---\n   432→\n   433→## business line two：Report Analysis\n   434→\n   435→### flow\n   436→\n   437→**entry**：`POST /chat/im/report`（aicenterapi）\n   438→\n   439→```\n   440→aicenterapi.ChatImReportLogic\n   441→  → hd_ai_search.ImReportApiProxy RPC\n   442→    → createsub-session IM group\n   443→    → send session_system(RUNNING) tomain session\n   444→    → send session_input tosub-session\n   445→    → return session_id\n   446→\n   447→IM callbacktrigger（sub-sessionreceiveto session_input）\n   448→  → HandleHDDIImCallback → handleSessionInputMsg → ImChat\n   449→    → executeReportBootstrapPipeline\n   450→      → R01（parsematerial）→ R01B（twophasecontentanalysis）‖ R02（personconfirm）\n   451→      → firstsend analysis_card，againsend user_choice_card tosub-session\n   452→      → send session_system(DONE) + session_card tomain session\n   453→```\n   454→\n   455→### reportanalysis Pipeline（R01B → R02）\n   456→\n   457→```\n   458→R01 parse report materials\n   459→  → R01B Phase1（JSON: user_message / findings / content_digest）\n   460→  → R01B Phase2（backend internally assembles active assumption associations）\n   461→  ‖ R02（JSON: identity_clues / match_candidates）\n   462→→ mergeresult → send IM card\n   463→```\n   464→\n   465→aftercontinued interaction（through IM typed callback）：\n   466→- `thread.report.person.identity_confirmed` → R03-b（buildfile）→ R04（reply ready）\n   467→- `thread.report.analysis_card_action_clicked` → analysis card button click\n   468→- `thread.report.analysis_angle_selected` → R05-R08（strategyswitch）\n   469→- `thread.report.reply_requested` → R09（reply draft）\n   470→- `thread.report.reply_tone_selected` → R10（style switch）（enum defined，stillnotregister callback）\n   471→- `thread.report.deep_talk_requested` → R12（deep chat opening）\n   472→\n   473→---\n   474→\n   475→## business line three：Article Analysis\n   476→\n   477→### flow\n   478→\n   479→**entry**：`POST /chat/im/article`（aicenterapi）"
