          result: "   479→**entry**：`POST /chat/im/article`（aicenterapi）\n   480→\n   481→```\n   482→aicenterapi.ChatImArticleLogic\n   483→  → hd_ai_search.ImArticleApiProxy RPC\n   484→    → createsub-session IM group\n   485→    → send session_system(RUNNING) tomain session\n   486→    → send session_input tosub-session\n   487→    → return session_id\n   488→\n   489→IM callbacktrigger（sub-sessionreceiveto session_input）\n   490→  → HandleHDDIImCallback → handleSessionInputMsg → ImChat\n   491→    → executeArticleBootstrapPipeline\n   492→      → ArticleSource → A01（associatedetermine）\n   493→      → send article_result tosub-session\n   494→      → send session_system(DONE) + session_card tomain session\n   495→```\n   496→\n   497→aftercontinued interaction（typed callback，by `services/partner/article/article_callback_dispatch.go` separatesend）：\n   498→- `thread.article.mode_selected` → `dispatchTypedArticleModeSelected` → A02 decide / forward / talk / stance\n   499→- `thread.article.action_clicked` → `dispatchTypedArticleActionClicked` → decision card action（patterntwo：keepOnlySelected，onlykeep selectedinbutton）\n   500→\n   501→articlesource：`article_content`（plain text）/ `article_url`（URL crawling）/ `hot_article_id`（hotarticle）。\n   502→\n   503→### articleModulefilestructure\n   504→\n   505→```\n   506→services/partner/article/\n   507→├── service.go                      ← Service setmeaning\n   508→├── facade.go                       ← outsidepartcallsentry\n   509→├── runtime.go                      ← runtime config\n   510→├── article_bootstrap.go            ← Bootstrap pipeline（ArticleSource → A01）\n   511→├── article_callback_dispatch.go    ← typed callback separatesend（mode_selected / action_clicked）\n   512→├── article_callback_mode.go        ← mode selectaftercardBuildwithsend\n   513→├── article_callback_assumption.go  ← decisionfalsesetpersistence\n   514→├── article_card_history.go         ← IM messagesnapshotloadwith disable logic\n   515→├── article_card_meta.go            ← cardelementdataencoding/decoding\n   516→├── article_im_msg_modify.go        ← IM messagemodify（disable + sync）\n   517→├── article_context_store.go        ← Redis onbelowtextstorage\n   518→├── article_task_manager.go         ← Pipeline taskmanagement\n   519→├── article_llm.go                  ← LLM callsencapsulate\n   520→├── article_prompt_templates.go     ← Prompt template\n   521→├── article_prompt_support.go       ← Prompt helpertool\n   522→├── article_boss_profile_prompt.go  ← bossprofile prompt Build\n   523→└── article_support.go              ← throughusehelperfunction\n   524→```\n   525→\n   526→---\n   527→\n   528→## IM callbackseparatestream\n   529→\n   530→### entry\n   531→\n   532→`callbackapi` → `HandleHDDIImCallback` → `imchat` withinpartialstream。\n   533→\n   534→### by CallbackCommand separatestream\n   535→\n   536→| CallbackCommand | process |\n   537→|-----------------|------|\n   538→| `Group.CallbackAfterSendMsg` | by `msg_type` twotimeseparatestream |\n   539→| `Group.CallbackAfterGroupInfoChanged` | returnwrite `chat_session.title` + main sessioncardtitle |\n   540→| `Group.CallbackAfterMemberExit` | sub-sessionsoftdelete + cardmark deleted |\n   541→\n   542→### message type secondary routing（AfterSendMsg）\n   543→\n   544→| msg_type | process |\n   545→|----------|------|\n   546→| `session_input` | → `ImChat`（bootstrap pipeline） |\n   547→| `chat` | recordlog |\n   548→| `thread.report.*` (6 kind) | → report typed dispatch |\n   549→| `thread.meeting.*` (3 kind) | → meeting typed dispatch |\n   550→| `thread.person.*` / `thread.assumption.*` | → thread memory action |\n   551→| `thread.article.*` (2 kind) | → article callback dispatch（`services/partner/article/`） |\n   552→| TIMTextElem rollback | → `ImChat`（transferforsingleentry user message） |\n   553→\n   554→placehas typed callback through `callback_registry.go` register。botmessage（`@RBT#` beforesuffix）in imchat withinjump。\n   555→\n   556→---\n   557→\n   558→## messageprotocol\n   559→\n   560→### session_system\n   561→\n   562→```json\n   563→{\"msg_type\": \"session_system\", \"session_id\": \"...\", \"session_type\": 2, \"title\": \"...\", \"status\": \"running\"}\n   564→```\n   565→\n   566→status：`running` → `done` / `failed`。through `ModifyGroupMessage` by `MsgSeq` originalgroundmodify。\n   567→\n   568→### session_card\n   569→\n   570→```json\n   571→{\"msg_type\": \"session_card\", \"session_id\": \"...\", \"session_type\": 2, \"title\": \"...\", \"payload\": {}}\n   572→```\n   573→\n   574→`MsgSeq` persistenceto `chat_session.main_session_card_msg_seq`，messagebodycacheto `im_msg_record`。\n   575→\n   576→### typing_state\n   577→\n   578→```json\n   579→{\"msg_type\": \"typing_state\", \"session_id\": \"...\", \"status\": \"typing|stop\", \"title\": \"...\"}\n   580→```\n   581→\n   582→OnlineOnly，notlanding history。\n   583→\n   584→### streaming inference wrapper\n   585→\n   586→`<reasoning>` start，`</reasoning>` end。if still inferring when stream ends, send fallback `</reasoning>`。\n   587→\n   588→---\n   589→\n   590→## dataLayer\n   591→\n   592→### Coretable\n   593→\n   594→| table | usepath |\n   595→|----|------|\n   596→| `meeting` | willmeeting metadata（title、status、type、session_id） |\n   597→| `speaker` | willmeeting speaker（ASR recognition） |\n   598→| `transcript` | willmeeting transcription text |"
