    - type: reasoning
      text: "Now I have a good understanding of the context. Let me now invoke the autoresearch skill as the user requested. But first, let me understand the user's request more clearly:\n\n1. When users submit articles (report/article), the system crawls the article content and returns it to the frontend\n2. Problem 1: The crawler doesn't always successfully return the article title\n3. Problem 2: The article content is in markdown format, which is hard to render nicely on the frontend\n4. Proposed solution: After crawling, pass the content through AI (beanpackage/Doubao model) to:\n   - Generate a title (if the crawler didn't get one)\n   - Generate a summary (summary) of no more than 100 characters\n   - Return these to the frontend as a fallback\n5. In the sub-session (sub-session), the article card currently shows raw markdown content - replace this with the AI-generated summary\n6. May need a new database column to store the summary\n\nThe user wants me to create a plan and has requested `/autoresearch Iterations: 10 ultrathink` - let me invoke the autoresearch skill with this approach."
