t analysis pipeline |\n   804→| `services/partner/article/` | article analysis pipeline（contain callback dispatch、card history、card meta） |\n   805→| `services/partner/common/` | shareduselogic（imhelper / persona / scenemeta / taskrunner / threadaction / toolruntime） |\n   806→| `services/thread_memory/` | person memoryservice |\n   807→| `services/boss_profile_memory/` | boss profile storage & sync |\n   808→| `services/qa/stream_chat/provider/` | LLM provider（contain test_provider.go） |\n   809→| `e2ebridge/` | E2E server bridgeLayer（DDL、mock RPC、ServiceContext） |\n   810→\n   811→### Tencent IM SDK\n   812→\n   813→| file | responsibility |\n   814→|------|------|\n   815→| `common/sdk/tencent/hddi_boss_bot/client_interface.go` | `IMClient` interface |\n   816→| `common/sdk/tencent/hddi_boss_bot/protocol/` | Message type definitions、encoding/decoding |\n   817→\n   818→### shared data source for frontend and backend\n   819→\n   820→| file | responsibility |\n   821→|------|------|\n   822→| `common/shared/reaction_emoji.json` | Emoji mapping（Go through `go:embed` compileembedenter，Frontenddirectly import） |\n   823→| `common/shared/reaction_emoji.go` | Go end Emoji parse + AI prompt generate |\n   824→| `common/shared/user_relation.json` | user relationship options（Go enum `THREAD_PERSON_RELATION` actionstategenerate，Frontenddirectly import） |\n   825→| `common/shared/user_relation.go` | Go endUser relationsparse |\n   826→\n   827→### Frontend\n   828→\n   829→| file | responsibility |\n   830→|------|------|\n   831→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/boss/api.ts` | Boss HTTP API calls |\n   832→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/boss/store.ts` | Boss Pinia store |\n   833→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/boss/record.ts` | Audio recording hook |\n   834→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/claw/api.ts` | IM API |\n   835→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/claw/store.ts` | Claw Pinia store（Composition API） |\n   836→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/claw/im/tim.ts` | TIM SDK singletonmanagement |\n   837→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/claw/im/group.ts` | groupoperation + messageconvert |\n   838→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/claw/im/config.ts` | group ID ↔ sessionId encoding/decoding |\n   839→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/hooks/useMeetingWebSocket.ts` | willmeeting WebSocket managementdevice |\n   840→| `packages-pc/hddr/src/router/routes.ts` | routebysetmeaning |\n   841→| `packages-harbor/harbor/src/enums/meeting.ts` | WebSocket messagetypeenum |\n   842→\n   843→---\n   844→\n   845→## developmentconstraint\n   846→\n   847→1. API Layershouldthin，notin API Layerimplement complex business\n   848→2. `user_id` mustfrom token get，notletFrontendpass\n   849→3. errorunified `hderror.NewErrorMsg(...)`\n   850→4. logs include function namebeforesuffix；error logs include parameters and `err`\n   851→5. nothandmodify `*.pb.go` and `types.go`\n   852→6. DB schema changestraceaddto `hddi_bot_migrate.sql`\n   853→7. `ImChat` pipeline withinnotsend RUNNING message——by `NotifyMeetingSessionRunning` raisebeforesendexit\n   854→8. actualwhen `EndMeeting`  `ImChat` mustasync，addquantity tick  `ImChat` mustsync\n   855→9. placehas `ImChat` callspoint failure mustcalls `MarkMeetingSessionFailed`\n   856→10. `IMClient` from `svcCtx.IMClient` readget，notuseusealllocalsingleton\n   857→11. notshouldconfused `message_id`（Frontend reaction）and `msg_seq`（serviceendmessagemodify）\n   858→12. Frontendimportthird-party UI componentuse `@hddr/components/...` don'tname\n   859→13. Frontend IM `session_id` throughconstantisafterend `topicId`/groupId，needwhenuse `encodeGroupIdToSessionId()` convert\n   860→\n   861→---\n   862→\n   863→## changesaftermust execute\n   864→\n   865→```bash\n   866→# proto changes\n   867→sh hd-ai-center/ai/hd_ai_search/bin/compile_grpc.sh hd-ai-center/ai/hd_ai_search/search.proto\n   868→\n   869→# api changes\n   870→sh hd-ai-center/apis/aicenterapi/bin/compile_api.sh\n   871→\n   872→# test\n   873→make test-go       # Go integration tests\n   874→make test-fe       # FrontendUnit tests\n   875→make